decks.notes: The main concept of this deck is to utilize the combo potential of Heliod, Sun-Crowned and Spike Feeder. The deck aims to generate a large amount of life gain and +1/+1 counters to create an unstoppable creature, while also having access to disruption and tutoring with cards like Eladamri's Call and Ranger-Captain of Eos. The deck also includes acceleration through Utopia Sprawl and Arbor Elf, as well as card advantage and creature selection with cards like Collected Company. The mana base is designed to provide a mix of green and white mana sources for optimal casting of the deck's spells.
